sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant UI as News List Page
    participant LW as Livewire Component
    participant DB as Database

    User->>UI: Open news list page
    UI->>LW: Initial request
    LW->>DB: Query articles (keywords, status, date range, sort)
    DB-->>LW: Paginated articles
    LW-->>UI: Render table and filters

    User->>UI: Search/filter/sort/paginate
    UI->>LW: Update bound properties
    LW->>DB: Re-query with conditions
    DB-->>LW: Updated page result
    LW-->>UI: Re-render list

    User->>UI: Delete article
    UI->>LW: deleteArticle(id)
    LW->>DB: Delete article row
    DB-->>LW: Deleted
    LW-->>UI: Success toast + refresh
